casebody.data:
Matthew STROJEK, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3804 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 10, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal from an order granting the state's motion in limine is dismissed for lack of jurisdiction. Appellant's motion to correct the record and motion for extension of time to file show cause order are denied as moot.

LaROSE, C.J., and VILLANTI and SALARIO, JJ., Concur.
